  "translations": {
    "en": "As for the sitting companion's right, treat him gently, be fair in discussion, do not leave without his permission. He who sits with you may leave without yours. Forget his slips, remember his good, let him hear only good. As for the neighbor's right, guard him absent, honour him present, help him when wronged. Do not pursue his faults; if you know evil, conceal it. If he accepts counsel, counsel privately. Do not abandon him in difficulty, forgive his sin, associate generously. There is no strength save in Allah.",
